  ('aboriginal-6f0ba476-moex-00557', 'aboriginal-6f0ba476', 'aboriginal-6f0ba476-moex-111-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-aboriginal-6f0ba476-08', NULL, 'single_choice', '在「李嘉圖恆等」理論下，若政府支出原來是以發行政府公債來融通，若現在改用課定額稅進行 融通，則下列何者正確？', '["民眾所得增加", "民眾所得減少", "民眾支出增加", "民眾支出不變"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:37:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7948d6976ec8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "db992a01dd7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111150", "c": "506", "s": "1111", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員特種考試外交領事人員及外交行政人員考試、民航人員考試、國際經濟商務人員考試、原住民族考試", "original_question_number": 22, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "aboriginal", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('aboriginal-6f0ba476-moex-00558', 'aboriginal-6f0ba476', 'aboriginal-6f0ba476-moex-111-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-aboriginal-6f0ba476-08', NULL, 'single_choice', '所謂的泰勒法則，是史丹佛大學的泰勒（JohnTaylor，1993），用美國1984年到1992年的資料所 估算出來的貨幣政策法則。泰勒發現美國聯邦準備銀行的貨幣政策，為採行釘住下列何項政策？', '["通貨膨脹率", "利率", "國民所得", "失業率"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:37:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7948d6976ec8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "db992a01dd7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111150", "c": "506", "s": "1111", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員特種考試外交領事人員及外交行政人員考試、民航人員考試、國際經濟商務人員考試、原住民族考試", "original_question_number": 23, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "aboriginal", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('aboriginal-6f0ba476-moex-00559', 'aboriginal-6f0ba476', 'aboriginal-6f0ba476-moex-111-d3ff7f6b', 'sub-aboriginal-6f0ba476-08', NULL, 'single_choice', '假定實質貨幣需求受利率及所得影響，貨幣需求的利率彈性為4，而貨幣需求的所得彈性為1。假 定利率沒有成長趨勢，而實質所得的成長趨勢為平均每年 6%。若政府欲將每年的通貨膨脹率維 持在2%以內的水準，則名目貨幣供給年增加率，必須控制在多少以內？', '["4%", "6%", "8%", "10%"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:37:57+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "7948d6976ec8", "answer_pdf_sha1": "db992a01dd7f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "111150", "c": "506", "s": "1111", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "經濟學", "year": "111", "exam_name": "111年公務人員特種考試外交領事人員及外交行政人員考試、民航人員考試、國際經濟商務人員考試、原住民族考試", "original_question_number": 24, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "aboriginal", "civil_category": "財稅行政"}'::jsonb, NULL)
